<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣١١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6257">مُعْتَمِرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1760">خَالِدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ بَعْضَ أُمَّهَاتِ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ اعْتَكَفَتْ وَهْيَ مُسْتَحَاضَةٌ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>